    e9 -->|"R9: reads CLAUDE.md, .claude/rules, auto-memory, skill frontmatter for ranking"| e4
    e9 -->|"R10: reads existing feedback + fact TOML during recall/list/show; writes new TOML during learn/remember/update"| e6
